                    <span>I work in a store and teach embroidery & digitizing, this is absolutely THE BEST primer for people just starting out in machine embroidery, and it's a great reference manual for everyone else. It is not machine-specific, so no matter what you've got, you will find information in here to help you out. This is THE book I always recommend to newbies!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not what I expected.</div>
                    <div>
