                    <span>I was new to machine embroidery and I happened to see this particular book lying on the store owners sewing desk.  I browsed through it and was immediately hooked!  I had to have my own copy. It has everything you could possibly need to know about machine embroidery.  I never did go back and do the classes for my machine...it was all in this book and then some!<br>The extra CD was a nice touch to the lessons!</span>
                  
